messages.subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] living my life
messages.messageBody:
<<There are alternative, code acceptable septic systems.
Mother Earth News magazine has adverizements and
addy's. Your homesteading list might have ideas.>>

Oh Yeah! I should ask them! LOL

<<House building is SLOW. You are doing GREAT. How is
your balcony garden?>>

My herbs (not herb) are doing well. Tomorrow I pick up my Tomatoes and
basil. I can taste the Bruschetta now. Mmmm. I better run to Home Depot
tonight and get some nice big containers !!
Also, I just talked to teh realtor. The first one failed, the second and
third passed but barely. The tester-man is going to do another more into the
woods where he expects it to pass. And if so, it won't even involve moving
the house site! So, it's not so bad. And we'll look at otehr lots in the
meantime.
I just want this one!!
Thank you Sharon, for the kind words.

Sharon of the Swamp
